    dc:creator "Zhao, Shuangyan; Liu, Cunqi; Hou, Zhonge" ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Description of a new species of Victoriopisa Karaman & Barnard, 1979 (Crustacea: Amphipoda: Eriopisidae) from China, with a key to the genus Victoriopisa" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263789>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263790>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263791>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263792>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263793>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263794> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263789>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Victoriopisa multiartus sp. nov., holotype, female (8.5 mm). A, body (lateral view); B, antenna I; C, accessory flagellum; D, antenna II; E, distal articles of antenna II; F, upper lip; G, lower lip." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/263789/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263790>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Victoriopisa multiartus sp. nov., female: C – H; male: A – B. A, left mandible; B, right mandible; C, maxilla I; D, maxilla II; E, outer plate of maxilla II; F, maxilliped; G, inner plate of maxilliped (to show three stout apical spines); H, telson." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/263790/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263791>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Victoriopisa multiartus sp. nov., female holotype. A, gnathopod I; B, propodus palm of gnathopod I; C, propodus of gnathopod I; D, gnathopod II; E, propodus of gnathopod II." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/263791/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263792>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Victoriopisa multiartus sp. nov., female holotype. A, pereopod III; B, dactylus of pereopod III; C, pereopod IV; D, dactylus of pereopod IV; E, pereopod V; F, dactylus of pereopod V; G, pereopod VI; H, distal dactylus of pereopod VI." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/263792/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263793>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Victoriopisa multiartus sp. nov., female holotype. A, pereopod VII; B, dactylus of pereopod VII; C, pleopod I; D, pleopod II; E, pleopod III; F, uropod I; G, uropod II; H, uropod III." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/263793/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263794>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Victoriopisa multiartus sp. nov., male paratype. A, gnathopod I (notice dactylus is missing); B, gnathopod II; C, pereopod VII." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/263794/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

